The yield on 30-day Bankers SecurityDeposit Accounts issued this week by the Saudi Arabian MonetaryAgency (SAMA) rose by more than 1/8 point to 5.95913 pct from5.79348 a week ago, bankers said.    SAMA decreased the offer price on the 900 mln riyal issueto 99.50586 from 99.51953 last Saturday. Like-dated interbankdeposits were quoted today at 6-3/8, 1/8 pct -- 1/8 pointhigher than last Saturday.    SAMA offers a total of 1.9 billion riyals in 30, 91 and180-day paper to banks in the kingdom each week. REUTER&#3;